<view class="container">
  <view class="header">
    <image class="logo" src="/images/logo.png" mode="aspectFit"></image>
    <text class="title">吃不吃</text>
    <text class="subtitle">毒舌减肥助手</text>
  </view>
  
  <view class="main-button-container">
    <button class="main-button" bindtap="onTakePhoto">
      <image class="camera-icon" src="/images/camera.png" mode="aspectFit"></image>
      <text>拍照识别</text>
    </button>
  </view>
  
  <view class="recent-history" wx:if="{{recentRecords.length > 0}}">
    <view class="section-title">最近记录</view>
    <view class="records-list">
      <view class="record-item" wx:for="{{recentRecords}}" wx:key="id" bindtap="onViewRecord" data-id="{{item.id}}">
        <image class="food-image" src="{{item.imageUrl}}" mode="aspectFill"></image>
        <view class="record-info">
          <text class="record-time">{{item.formattedTime}}</text>
          <text class="record-feedback">{{item.feedback.sarcasticComment}}</text>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
  
  <view class="empty-state" wx:else>
    <image class="empty-illustration" src="/images/empty_plate.png" mode="aspectFit"></image>
    <text class="empty-text">还没有记录</text>
    <view class="harsh-tip">别浪费时间了！赶紧拍照，让我看看你今天又想吃什么垃圾食品。不要再拖延了，你的健康状况等不起！</view>
  </view>
</view> 